# Device configuration
# Format: ADDRESS [PROTOCOL]
#
# PROTOCOL: ble (default) or classic
#
# Examples:
#   AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF              # BLE device (default)
#   AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF ble          # BLE device (explicit)
#   AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF classic      # Classic Bluetooth device
#
# To pair a new device:
#   python main.py --pair --protocol classic
#
# Only the first non-comment line is used.

# 98:B9:EA:01:67:68 classic
